title: adidas Originals | Superstar 80s by GONZ
description: Mark Gonzales has always gone against the grain and blazed his own path. If it wasn’t for The Gonz doing it his way, skateboarding would be way different. It is this pioneering spirit that adidas Originals pays homage to with their latest collaboration – the #Superstar 80s by Gonz.
